### Get all ingredients
GET localhost:8080/ingredients

### Get ingredient by ID
GET localhost:8080/ingredients/6


### Get stock value at specific time
GET localhost:8080/ingredients/1/stock?at=2024-06-01T12:00:00Z&unit=KG

### Get all dishes
GET localhost:8080/dishes


### Associate ingredients to dish (replace all existing ingredients)
PUT localhost:8080/dishes/1/ingredients
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "ingredient": {
      "id": 1000
    },
    "quantity_required": 2.5,
    "unit": "KG"
  },
  {
    "ingredient": {
      "id": 3
    },
    "quantity_required": 1,
    "unit": "PCS"
  },
  {
    "ingredient": {
      "id": 5
    },
    "quantity_required": 30,
    "unit": "PCS"
  }
]

### Dissociate all ingredients from dish (empty list)
PUT localhost:8080/dishes/1/ingredients
Content-Type: application/json

[]

### f) GET Movements avec filtre (Remplace l'ID 1 par un ID existant)
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/1/stockMovements?from=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-12-31T23:59:59Z


### g) POST Movements (Ajout de nouveaux flux)
POST http://localhost:8080/ingredients/1/stockMovements
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "type": "IN",
    "value": {
      "quantity": 50.0,
      "unit": "KG"
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "OUT",
    "value": {
      "quantity": 10.0,
      "unit": "KG"
    }
  }
]

### Test Erreur 404 (ID inexistant)
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/9999/stockMovements?from=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-12-31T23:59:59Z